gov.nih.nlm.mrd.common
Class ReleaseTarget

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.mrd.common.ReleaseTarget
public class ReleaseTarget
extends Object

Represents a release target. Each target is associated with a release handler on the server side that performs the build/validate/publish tasks.

Author:
MRD Group
